Well, I'm sure it'll be fine.

553
00:41:49,317 --> 00:41:53,317
明日からもいい日が続きそうだ。
Looks like good days will continue from tomorrow too.

554
00:41:55,117 --> 00:41:58,617
あ、UFO！
Oh, a UFO!

555
