859
00:59:13,670 --> 00:59:15,170
はい！
Yes!

860
00:59:15,636 --> 00:59:17,670
一番ムズ！難しい。
That's the hardest! Difficult.

861
00:59:18,070 --> 00:59:19,636
その心は？
And the answer?

862
00:59:21,670 --> 00:59:28,203
ピコハンとかけまして、ししろんと解く。その心は…
Picohan and Shishiron. The answer is...

863
00:59:39,170 --> 00:59:45,171
どちらも…戦闘力が…100万！
Both have a combat power of... ONE MILLION!

864
00:59:55,671 --> 00:59:58,171
一滑りプレゼントします！
Here's a joke that fell flat for you!

865
01:00:00,165 --> 01:00:40,565
モノボケ撮影会！？
Prop Comedy Photoshoot!?

866
01:00:01,198 --> 01:00:02,465
